                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9828" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1488</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1246 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">开普云数据资产管理的先锋探索之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Pioneer Exploration Path of Data Asset Management in Ucap</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">林红珍，王曹逸</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">开普云信息科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">开普云；数据资产管理；三权分置；确认与计量；合规管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ucap；Data Asset Management; Separation of Three Rights; Recognition and Measurement; Compliance Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在数字经济背景下，国家相继出台了一系列政策加速推动数据资源资产化，并鼓励企业对数据资产高效管理。本案例描述了开普云作为AGI时代全栈AI产品服务提供商，是如何对数据资源进行会计确认与计量，完成数据资源到数据资产的转化，获得“数据加工使用权证书”，并积极投身于数据资产的合规管理。开普云凭借自身的创新实践，开辟出一条契合企业自身发展的数据资产管理路径，积极宣贯国际标准ISO 55013《资产管理数据资产管理指南》，对其企业实行数据全生命周期的管理，成为首批国际标准实践示范案例单位，是数据资产管理领域的先锋探索者。本案例可应用于会计学、管理会计等课程的教学中，使学生深刻理解在大数据时代，企业应根据自身特点精准选择数据资源，进行规范的会计确认与计量，并了解强化数据资产的合规管理是提升数据资产管理效能的关键所在。本案例旨在通过案例分析，使学生了解企业数据资产的含义及类型，在《企业数据资源相关会计处理暂行规定》框架下如何对数据资产进行确认和计量、如何加强数据资产合规管理，培养学生的数据思维，深入理解数据资产作为企业新型生产要素的战略价值，掌握数据资产全生命周期管理的核心方法论，为数字经济时代培养既懂会计专业知识又具备数据素养的复合型人才奠定坚实基础。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Abstract:In the context of the digital economy, the state has successively introduced a series of policies to accelerate the assetization of data resources and encourage enterprises to manage data assets efficiently. This case study describes how Capinfo, as a full-stack AI product and service provider in the AGI era, has carried out accounting recognition and measurement of data resources, transformed data resources into data assets, obtained the &quot;Data Processing Usage Certificate&quot;, and actively engaged in the compliance management of data assets. Capinfo, through its own innovative practices, has blazed a trail for data asset management that suits its own development, actively promoted the international standard ISO 55013 &quot;Guidelines for Data Asset Management in Asset Management&quot;, implemented full life-cycle management of data for its enterprises, and became one of the first demonstration units for the implementation of international standards. It is a pioneer in the exploration of data asset management. This case can be applied in the teaching of accounting and management accounting courses, enabling students to deeply understand that in the era of big data, enterprises should precisely select data resources based on their own characteristics, carry out standardized accounting recognition and measurement, and understand that strengthening the compliance management of data assets is the key to improving the efficiency of data asset management. This case study aims to enable students to understand the meaning and types of enterprise data assets through case analysis, how to recognize and measure data assets under the framework of the &quot;Interim Provisions on Accounting Treatment of Enterprise Data Resources&quot;, how to strengthen the compliance management of data assets, cultivate students&#39; data thinking, deeply understand the strategic value of data assets as a new type of production factor for enterprises, master the core methodology of the full life cycle management of data assets, and lay a solid foundation for cultivating compound talents who are proficient in accounting professional knowledge and possess data literacy in the era of digital economy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数据资产定义、类型与特性;数据资产的确认和计量;三权分置;数据资产合规与风控管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
